quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  58,1,Kad semiÂṀallahu kavlelletiy tucadiluke fiy zevciha ve teÅtekiy ilellahi vallahu yesmeÂṀu tehavurekuma innallahe semiyÂṀun basÄḟyrun
  58,2,Elleziyne yuzahirune minkum min nisaihim ma hunne ummehatihim in ummehatuhum ilellaiy velednehum ve innehum leyekulune munkeren minelkavli ve zuren ve innallahe leÂṀafuvvun Äafurun
  58,3,Velleziyne yuzahirune min nisaihim summe yeÂṀudune lima kalu fetahriyru rekabetin min kabli en yetemassa zalikum tuÂṀazune bihi vallahu bima taÂṀmelune habiyrun
  58,4,Femen lem yecid fesÄḟyamu Åehreyni mutetabiÂṀayni min kabli en yetemassa femen lem yestetÄḟÂṀ feÄḟtÂṀamu sittiyne miskiynen zalike lituÂṀminu billahi ve resulihi ve tilke hududullahi ve lilkafiriyne ÂṀazabun eliymun
  58,5,ÄḞnnelleziyne yuhaddunallahe ve resulehu kubitu kema kubitelleziyne min kablihim ve kad enzelna ayatin beyyinatin v uhumullahu cemiyÂṀan feyunebbiuhum bima ÂṀamilu ahsahullahu ve nesuhu e lilkafiriyne ÂṀazabun muhiynun
  58,6,Yevme yebÂṀas vallahu ÂṀala kulli ÅeyÂṀin Åehiydun